        <div>
          <h4>Orange County mainstream</h4>
          <p>Anaheim · Santa Ana · Orange · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a> · Garden Grove · Fullerton · Tustin</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ventura mid-market</h4>
          <p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Simi Valley · Oxnard · Ventura · Camarillo</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Inland Empire family housing</h4>
          <p>Ontario · <a href="/rancho-cucamonga/">Rancho Cucamonga</a> · Riverside · Fontana · Moreno Valley · Murrieta · Corona</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related GE and Haier-family pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/ge-profile-refrigerator-repair/">GE Profile refrigerator repair →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/ge-cafe-refrigerator-repair/">GE Café refrigerator repair →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/ge-monogram-refrigerator-repair/">GE Monogram refrigerator repair →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/haier-refrigerator-repair/">Haier refrigerator repair (Haier-branded compact) →</a></li>
